# Omelette Backend Standards

- Use Python 3.12+ features (type hints, StrEnum, match-case)
- All database operations use async SQLAlchemy with `AsyncSession`
- Pydantic v2 for all request/response schemas
- Follow FastAPI dependency injection pattern via `app/api/deps.py`
- LLM calls go through `app/services/llm_client.py` — never call OpenAI directly
- All API responses use `ApiResponse[T]` wrapper from `app/schemas/common.py`
- Background tasks use `Task` model for tracking progress
- Run `conda activate omelette` before any Python command
- Data files go to `/data0/djx/omelette/`, code stays in `/home/djx/repos/omelette/`
